Package: linux-headers-raspi${variant:suffix}
Architecture: armhf arm64
Section: kernel
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, linux-headers-${kernel-abi-version}-raspi
Description: Raspberry Pi Linux kernel headers
 This package will always depend on the latest Raspberry Pi Linux
 kernel headers available.

Package: linux-image-raspi${variant:suffix}
Architecture: armhf arm64
Section: kernel
